<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1503133-i-haven-t-read-this-book-but-is-the">I haven&#39;t read this book, but is the character, Roseanne McNulty, an allegory for Ireland itself? That&#39;s what I gather from the synopsis. If answering would result in spoilers, then I guess I&#39;d rather not know.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1503133'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F3419808-the-secret-scripture">like</a></span>

