              <span id="reviewTextContainer2631293888" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6721573192431924556">I absolutely loved this. Barry is such a wonderful writer. This novel is full of real characters and fascinating snapshots of history, with a fantastic plot.</span>

